 <th class="text-center p-3 font-black uppercase text-xs">Ciclos (80% cap.)</th>
 <th class="text-center p-3 font-black uppercase text-xs">Trazabilidad</th>
 <th class="text-center p-3 font-black uppercase text-xs">Precio Relativo</th>
 <th class="text-left p-3 font-black uppercase text-xs">Recomendado para</th>
 </tr>
